  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/ed4c38188b9afc0cf458124d8994d4c7.avif?t=1773103826\" width=600 height=222 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/85af7187950124c6151728bf6a05046b.poster.avif?t=1773103826\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/85af7187950124c6151728bf6a05046b.webm?t=1773103826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/85af7187950124c6151728bf6a05046b.mp4?t=1773103826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/daf0f1e10da5459b8b7eb0456231defa.webp?t=1773103826\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/5d12bb967ba0bbcc000d005cda9a025c.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/a400525afbd4bb47c6d851a745d3384a.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=23 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a spine-chilling adventure with <strong>The Other Side</strong>, a gripping 1-6 player cooperative ghost hunting experience that pushes the boundaries of fear and excitement. Developed using the latest graphics technology available in Unreal Engine 5, this game offers a visually stunning and immersive journey into the supernatural. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>Unreal Engine 5's</strong> cutting-edge capabilities, <strong>The Other Side</strong> delivers unparalleled realism, from the eerie glow of ghostly apparitions to the atmospheric details of haunted environments.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/5d12bb967ba0bbcc000d005cda9a025c.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/064ee2a5c3915d14805c867e81165546.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=23 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team up with friends or brave the unknown alone as you venture into haunted locations teeming with restless spirits. Communication and teamwork are key as you work together to uncover the mysteries that lie on \"The Other Side.\"</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In-Game Voice Chat:</strong><br>Stay connected with your team using in-game voice chat. Communication is crucial as you share discoveries, coordinate movements, and react to unexpected paranormal encounters in real-time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combine Earned Equipment:</strong><br>Pool your resources and combine earned equipment to enhance your collective ghost-hunting capabilities. A successful job depends on the synergy of your customized gear, making every team member's contribution integral to unraveling the supernatural mysteries.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/5d12bb967ba0bbcc000d005cda9a025c.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/5601a86d3be3ce40efe15efd988955b6.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=23 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vehicle Upgrades:</strong><br>Utilize the extensive progression system to unlock custom materials, a spectrum of colors, and specialized equipment to aid in your jobs. Personalize your vehicle to reflect your unique ghost-hunting style and ensure you're well-equipped to face the unknown on this chilling journey.\"<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/f346db47eec511f98efa326656dfb935.poster.avif?t=1773103826\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/f346db47eec511f98efa326656dfb935.webm?t=1773103826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/f346db47eec511f98efa326656dfb935.mp4?t=1773103826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Customization:</strong><br>Purchase a new look for your character with a full range of apparel, hair, skin tone.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/0231f970d7d2ce14fff590d7b2e1cda8.poster.avif?t=1773103826\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/0231f970d7d2ce14fff590d7b2e1cda8.webm?t=1773103826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/0231f970d7d2ce14fff590d7b2e1cda8.mp4?t=1773103826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Equipment Progression:</strong><br>Purchase new equipment as you advance in your ghost hunting career. Give yourself an edge and be the lead contributor to your crew's stash.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Headquarters Outfitting:</strong><br>Unleash your creativity as you furnish and upgrade your base, sculpting its appearance to reflect your success in completing contracts and tasks. Create an atmospheric hub that fellow ghost hunters envy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/351b0c441ed720187c9dfb56bfb34fa7.poster.avif?t=1773103826\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/351b0c441ed720187c9dfb56bfb34fa7.webm?t=1773103826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/351b0c441ed720187c9dfb56bfb34fa7.mp4?t=1773103826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/5d12bb967ba0bbcc000d005cda9a025c.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/e401baa1016da102b6f821f3fe36bb1c.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=23 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Identify</strong>:<br>Unravel the enigma surrounding each ghost by gathering clues and piecing together their stories. Use advanced ghost-hunting gadgets to detect anomalies and unveil the truth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cleanse</strong>:<br>Confront malevolent spirits in intense paranormal encounters. Coordinate with your team to cleanse haunted areas, facing escalating challenges that demand quick thinking and courage. Use your Spectral Affixer to find the ghost's characteristics, and locate the bound item.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/5d12bb967ba0bbcc000d005cda9a025c.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/107151c9e49c0149b3bf901abf24c751.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=23 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a variety of hauntingly atmospheric locations, each with its own dark history and unique challenges. From decrepit mansions to abandoned asylums, every environment is meticulously crafted to deliver an immersive ghost-hunting experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2764750/extras/5d12bb967ba0bbcc000d005cda9a025c.webp?t=1773103826\" width=616 height=5 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to face what awaits on \"The Other Side\"? Gather your team, gear up, and step into the unknown. The spirits are waiting..</strong></p>",
